  "response": "A suitable inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center in Calhoun County, Alabama, is the Anniston Fellowship House Inc. Here are some key details about this facility:\n\n- **Name:** Anniston Fellowship House Inc\n- **Address:** 106 12th Street, Anniston, AL 36201\n- **Phone:** (256) 236-7017\n- **Services Offered:** Inpatient treatment for substance abuse, individual and group counseling, relapse prevention, and aftercare planning.\n- **Payment Options:** Accepts various insurance plans, as well as self-payment.\n\nIt's important to verify the current status and specific services of the center, as these can change. You may want to call them directly or visit their website for the most up-to-date information. Additionally, consider reaching out to local health departments or addiction specialists for further recommendations and guidance tailored to individual needs.",
